{"tid":366354,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[廉航香港快運] 發覺班UO撚好鍾意拎獨有航點來打J","createTime":"2017-08-20T03:20:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-20T16:26:43.000Z","uid":42188,"like":17,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"88db961c447d74a348306d9640385ca498bf3c15","tid":366354,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T03:20:51.000Z","msg":"講明先，此post非針對所有廉航，只針對UO<br />\n班UO撚好鍾意拎廣島同石垣來打J<br />\n每次一有人狙擊快運，總有人衝出來話: 「我想去廣島/石垣島，唔坐快運可以坐乜？」<br />\n其實都係藉此俾自己一個心靈安慰，覺得自己坐廉航係因為得UO先有直航，而唔係窮先要坐UO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢班UO撚講到唔坐直航會死咁，但年中都唔知有幾多UO撚坐UO去東京再轉飛去新千歲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n事實證明根本唔關係咪直航事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4b2f9e8a9855dc21c9f510f6f995814bf41322f","tid":366354,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T05:25:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 2個UO撚偷偷放下負評"},{"pid":"e1eea24b4cc95a760d4508e337f68e9f411ae1b2","tid":366354,"uid":33703,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T08:18:06.000Z","msg":"除左坐uo之外 教我點樣即日來回福岡 thanks"},{"pid":"b3544c02f0608cc385f3c184ce784cfbde22bc5e","tid":366354,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T09:58:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>除左坐uo之外 教我點樣即日來回福岡 thanks</blockquote><br />\n無架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我長知識了，UO撚又多一個理據用來打J <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c97983210914b48c1c716f30704b809da7dcd5c","tid":366354,"uid":2146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T10:02:20.000Z","msg":"出事咪見真章<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a3588a4c6b6ff256f43be0ab4d7d07d079eeb0f","tid":366354,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T10:05:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>除左坐uo之外 教我點樣即日來回福岡 thanks</blockquote><br />\n無架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我長知識了，UO撚又多一個理據用來打J <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n石恆 on9窮閪先去 咪撚扮深度遊 如果3千蚊張機票班撚樣仲會唔會去?"},{"pid":"033a989f2c906a04e12b7a2eedaf2d5e6d9942c7","tid":366354,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T11:05:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>除左坐uo之外 教我點樣即日來回福岡 thanks</blockquote><br />\n無架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我長知識了，UO撚又多一個理據用來打J <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n石恆 on9窮閪先去 咪撚扮深度遊 如果3千蚊張機票班撚樣仲會唔會去?</blockquote><br />\n咪踢爆d窮閪啦<br />\n用札幌做例子<br />\n唔坐CX啦，HX直航機票$3k都話貴<br />\n要坐UO去東京轉內陸機去札幌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另一方面就話人地唔坐廉航直航係on9 (eg廣島/高松)"},{"pid":"3d5b03bb0e8347708e604863226531c14c711d92","tid":366354,"uid":60219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T11:43:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>除左坐uo之外 教我點樣即日來回福岡 thanks</blockquote><br />\n無架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我長知識了，UO撚又多一個理據用來打J <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n石恆 on9窮閪先去 咪撚扮深度遊 如果3千蚊張機票班撚樣仲會唔會去?</blockquote><br />\n咪踢爆d窮閪啦<br />\n用札幌做例子<br />\n唔坐CX啦，HX直航機票$3k都話貴<br />\n要坐UO去東京轉內陸機去札幌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">另一方面就話人地唔坐廉航直航係on9 (eg廣島/高松)</span></blockquote><br />\n紅字有咩唔啱<br />\n以前未有UO，我由香港去四國要去on99去關西機場轉，一來一回好浪費時間<br />\n當時如果有高松航點我一定搭UO"},{"pid":"044b0f44495223c051d695c68d8ad28bce9d6636","tid":366354,"uid":42188,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T11:54:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>除左坐uo之外 教我點樣即日來回福岡 thanks</blockquote><br />\n無架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我長知識了，UO撚又多一個理據用來打J <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n石恆 on9窮閪先去 咪撚扮深度遊 如果3千蚊張機票班撚樣仲會唔會去?</blockquote><br />\n咪踢爆d窮閪啦<br />\n用札幌做例子<br />\n唔坐CX啦，HX直航機票$3k都話貴<br />\n要坐UO去東京轉內陸機去札幌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">另一方面就話人地唔坐廉航直航係on9 (eg廣島/高松)</span></blockquote><br />\n紅字有咩唔啱<br />\n以前未有UO，我由香港去四國要去on99去關西機場轉，一來一回好浪費時間<br />\n當時如果有高松航點我一定搭UO</blockquote><br />\n啲UO撚講到冇直航會死，CX撚話去廣島可以先飛福岡再買pass轉新幹線去廣島，然後俾UO撚話on9，但UO撚去札幌就轉機，證明係咪直航根本唔係重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"924c04c4ae0d9d85dfd4e5a1ab2cb3a42c6a4820","tid":366354,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T16:26:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>